  "comment": "Octostrip FLEX 0.5m: Octostrip FLEX - 0.5m is an IP65-rated RGBW strip with 4 controllable sections and a maximum power of 14 watts. It has a robust aluminium housing that also helps with convection cooling of the LEDs. Available accessories include black and white covers that also work as diffusers and cables in various lengths.\nThis is not a standalone LED strip, it must be controlled by the Showtec Controller for Octostrip FLEX.",
